&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'SimSun'; font-size:9pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;使用说明:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'SimSun'; font-size:9pt;&quot;&gt;1. 选择目标轴，点击&amp;quot;从驱动器读取&amp;quot;获取当前参数&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'SimSun'; font-size:9pt;&quot;&gt;2. 修改参数值，点击&amp;quot;写入驱动器&amp;quot;使参数生效(RAM)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'SimSun'; font-size:9pt;&quot;&gt;3. 如需断电保持，点击&amp;quot;保存到Flash&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'SimSun'; font-size:9pt; color:#ff0000;&quot;&gt;注意: Pn065(位置环增益1)为粗调，范围0-24；Pn063(位置环增益2)为细调，范围1000-5000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
